{"tid":2067179,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"來開始魔界的特訓吧！幽☆遊☆特茶 !!","createTime":"2020-06-16T21:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T21:52:44.000Z","uid":229397,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f96f2eb0796f483ca0f88050c200a9c70d96f8","tid":2067179,"uid":229397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T21:52:45.000Z","msg":"日本食品大廠「三得利」在今日（15）與人氣漫畫《幽遊白書》開始合作企劃組成了「幽☆遊☆特茶」並準備了兩項活動「幽☆遊☆特チャット」與「戸愚呂が教える＃今のおまえに足りないもの」來與你度過健康的夏日！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/159219366599.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F159219366599.jpeg&h=479bd1ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本次企劃的第一個活動「幽☆遊☆特チャット」 是在LINE上公開，只要加入「伊右衛門 特茶」的官方LINE帳號並開始聊天，輸入想要鍛鍊的內容就會有幽助、桑原、飛影、藏馬等角色給你適當的鍛鍊建議。<br />\n▼根據以下的方式操作，讓靈界與魔界的各位來教你如何鍛鍊健康身材！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/159219371697.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F159219371697.jpeg&h=bfb55c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼每次回答都有不同的人來提供你建議~~<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/159219383635.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F159219383635.jpeg&h=4d2aaf90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/159219385350.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F159219385350.jpeg&h=94c9933a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而第二個活動「戸愚呂が教える＃今のおまえに足りないもの」 則是在推特上公開，只要到「伊右衛門 特茶」的官方推特的推文中選擇你認為今天缺少的東西並轉推，戶愚呂就會解放百分之百的力量來給你最有利的答案。<br />\n▼ 戶愚呂的100%超強力建議！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/159219415997.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F159219415997.jpeg&h=ea63e6d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/159219417553.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F159219417553.jpeg&h=4b925b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/159219420427.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F159219420427.jpeg&h=fc7e4bff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，完成訓練的人可以獲得活動贈與的手機桌布，在活動官網上也可以下載網路視訊會議用的虛擬背景。覺得夏日不想渾渾噩噩懶在家裡的朋友們，現在就快點行動與幽助他們一起鍛鍊出強健的體魄吧！<br />\n▼ 完成訓練後能下載手機桌布來使用（共14種，以下為部分）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/159219438219.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F159219438219.jpeg&h=eca44e56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/159219439549.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F159219439549.jpeg&h=b813dcfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/15921943624.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F15921943624.jpeg&h=85df3087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YBn75yn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYBn75yn.jpg&h=d6bbcb17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mhzqSdL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmhzqSdL.jpg&h=e6269c7e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n▼ 官網?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.suntory.co.jp/softdrink/iyemon/tokucha/yuyutokucha/?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=click&amp;utm_content=1&amp;utm_campaign=yuyuhakusho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.suntory.co.jp%2Fsoftdrink%2Fiyemon%2Ftokucha%2Fyuyutokucha%2F%3Futm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_medium%3Dclick%26utm_content%3D1%26utm_campaign%3Dyuyuhakusho&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG25pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=04aa4cfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.suntory.co.jp/softdrink/iyemon/tokucha/yuyutokucha/?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=click&amp;utm_content=1&amp;utm_campaign=yuyuhakusho</a>"}]}